OL,3,CMayor admits stalking after sending
OL,4,Cunwanted love letters to the wrong
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,FThe mayor of Whitehaven has today
OL,8,Fadmitted two counts of stalking after
OL,9,Fsending unwanted love letters to the
OL,10,Fwrong woman.
OL,12,FGraham Roberts, 72, used his position
OL,13,Fas a councillor to access the address
OL,14,Fof a woman who worked in his local
OL,15,Fpub, but sent them to the wrong person.
OL,17,FWhitehaven Town Council confirmed
OL,18,FRoberts stepped down from his position
OL,19,Fas mayor in September due to health
OL,20,Freasons, but he has not resigned and
OL,21,Fstill formally holds the position.
