OL,4,Cunwanted love letters to the wrong
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,FWorkington magistrates' court heard
OL,8,Fhow the woman who received the letters
OL,9,Fwas shocked to read unsolicited
OL,10,Fcomments about her figure and
OL,11,Feducation, also suggesting that she
OL,12,Fwas his 'soulmate'. The crimes took
OL,13,Fplace between 27 August and 12
OL,14,FSeptember 2024.
OL,16,FThe victim changed her routine and
OL,17,Fstopped running at night in fear of
OL,18,Ffeeling someone was watching her.
