OL,3,CMayor admits stalking after sending
OL,4,Cunwanted love letters to the wrong
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,FShe said: "I have been feeling very
OL,8,Fanxious and on edge. I have been
OL,9,Fconstantly looking out of my window at
OL,10,Fnight to see if there is anyone there."
OL,12,FShe found out who the letters were
OL,13,Ffrom after receiving a business card
OL,14,Ffrom Roberts.
OL,16,FFollowing his arrest, he admitted that
OL,17,Fhe sent the letters thinking it was
OL,18,Fthe woman from his local pub.
