OL,3,CMayor admits stalking after sending
OL,4,Cunwanted love letters to the wrong
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,FThe intended recipient of the letters
OL,8,Ftold the police that Roberts had
OL,9,Fcontinually asked to date her despite
OL,10,Fsaying no.
OL,12,FIn her victim impact statement, she
OL,13,Fsaid: "This incident has left me
OL,14,Ffeeling nervous and I no longer wish
OL,15,Fto see Graham in my place of work or
OL,16,Fcome across him at all due to his
OL,17,Fbehaviour.
