OL,3,CMayor admits stalking after sending
OL,4,Cunwanted love letters to the wrong
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,F"I want Graham to understand that his
OL,8,Fbehaviour is unwanted and frankly odd
OL,9,Fand do not wish him to behave with
OL,10,Fanyone else in such a way."
OL,12,FRachel Parker, Senior Crown Prosecutor
OL,13,Ffor CPS North West, said: "Graham
OL,14,FRoberts' actions have caused two women
OL,15,Fa lot of anxiety and distress.
OL,17,F"After becoming infatuated with a
OL,18,Fwoman, he abused his position as a
OL,19,Fcouncillor to access confidential
OL,20,Frecords to try and find her address.
