OL,3,CMayor admits stalking after sending
OL,4,Cunwanted love letters to the wrong
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,F"He displayed obsessive conduct with
OL,8,Fthe woman in his local pub and his
OL,9,Fbehaviour escalated when he began
OL,10,Fsending love letters to the wrong
OL,11,Faddress.
OL,13,F"The impact of Roberts' behaviour is
OL,14,Fclear; both women were uncomfortable
OL,15,Fand anxious, and one woman was forced
OL,16,Fto change her daily routines, leaving
OL,17,Fher paranoid and mistrusting of others
OL,18,Fin her life.
