OL,3,CMayor admits stalking after sending
OL,4,Cunwanted love letters to the wrong
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,F"The Crown Prosecution Service does
OL,8,Fnot underestimate the serious and
OL,9,Flasting impact stalking can have on
OL,10,Fvictims and will not hesitate to
OL,11,Fprosecute these cases where there is
OL,12,Fsufficient evidence to do so."
OL,14,FRoberts was given a 12-month community
OL,15,Forder, a 10-day rehabilitation
OL,16,Frequirement and fined #294 after
OL,17,Fpleading guilty to two counts of
OL,18,Fstalking, at Workington Magistrates
OL,19,FCourt on 6 May 2025.
